<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8"/>
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
<title>Terms of Use – Breathon</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Tajawal:wght@300;400;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
<style>
  :root {
    --blue: rgba(59,158,255,1);
    --blue-dim: rgba(59,158,255,0.15);
    --blue-faint: rgba(59,158,255,0.06);
    --text: rgba(255,255,255,0.85);
    --text-dim: rgba(255,255,255,0.45);
    --text-faint: rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
    --bg: #02040e;
    --border: rgba(255,255,255,0.07);
  }
  * { margin:0; padding:0; box-sizing:border-box; }
  body {
    background: var(--bg);
    color: var(--text);
    font-family: 'Tajawal', -apple-system, sans-serif;
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 1.8;
    min-height: 100vh;
  }
  body::before {
    content:'';
    position:fixed;
    top:-200px; left:50%;
    transform:translateX(-50%);
    width:600px; height:600px;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(59,158,255,0.07) 0%, transparent 70%);
    pointer-events:none;
    z-index:0;
  }
  .wrap {
    max-width: 680px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 56px 28px 72px;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }
  .header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 44px;
  }
  .header img { width:72px; height:72px; object-fit:contain; margin-bottom:14px; display:block; margin:0 auto 14px; }
  .app-name { font-size:0.72rem; letter-spacing:0.25em; text-transform:uppercase; color:var(--blue); margin-bottom:10px; font-weight:500; }
  h1 { font-size:1.7rem; font-weight:700; color:#fff; margin-bottom:8px; }
  .updated { font-size:0.75rem; color:var(--text-faint); }
  .divider { width:36px; height:1px; background:var(--blue-dim); margin:20px auto 0; }
  .section { margin-bottom:32px; border-top:1px solid var(--border); padding-top:24px; }
  h2 { font-size:0.95rem; font-weight:700; color:#fff; margin-bottom:10px; }
  p { font-size:0.86rem; color:var(--text-dim); line-height:1.9; margin-bottom:8px; }
  p:last-child { margin-bottom:0; }
  ul { list-style:none; margin:8px 0; }
  ul li { font-size:0.86rem; color:var(--text-dim); line-height:1.9; padding-left:16px; position:relative; }
  ul li::before { content:'·'; position:absolute; left:4px; color:var(--blue); }
  a { color:var(--blue); text-decoration:none; }
  a:hover { text-decoration:underline; }
  .footer { text-align:center; margin-top:52px; padding-top:28px; border-top:1px solid var(--border); }
  .footer img { width:38px; height:38px; object-fit:contain; display:block; margin:0 auto 8px; }
  .footer p { font-size:0.72rem; color:var(--text-faint); }
  .footer-links { display:flex; justify-content:center; gap:20px; margin-top:12px; }
  .footer-links a { font-size:0.72rem; color:var(--text-faint); }
  .footer-links a:hover { color:var(--blue); }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="wrap">
  <div class="header">
    <img src="data:image/png;base64," alt="Breathon"/>
    <div class="app-name">Breathon</div>
    <h1>Terms of Use</h1>
    <div class="updated">Effective Date: March 25, 2026</div>
    <div class="divider"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <h2>Acceptance of Terms</h2>
    <p>By downloading or using Breathon, you agree to these Terms. If you do not agree, please do not use the app.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <h2>Subscriptions & Payments</h2>
    <p>Breathon offers the following auto-renewable subscriptions:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong style="color:#fff">Breathon Monthly</strong> — $4.99 per month</li>
      <li><strong style="color:#fff">Breathon Yearly</strong> — $29.99 per year (~$2.50/month)</li>
    </ul>
    <p>Payment is charged to your Apple ID at confirmation of purchase. Subscriptions automatically renew unless cancelled at least 24 hours before the end of the current period. Manage or cancel anytime in your App Store settings. No refunds for unused portions.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <h2>Free Trial</h2>
    <p>If a free trial is offered, you will be automatically charged at the end of the trial unless cancelled beforehand. Only one free trial per Apple ID.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <h2>Health Disclaimer</h2>
    <p>Breathon is for relaxation and mindfulness only. It is not a medical device and is not intended to diagnose, treat, or prevent any condition. Consult a healthcare professional before starting any new wellness practice.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>Questions? Reach us at <a href="mailto:breathonapp@gmail.com">breathonapp@gmail.com</a></p>
    <p><a href="https://breathonapp.github.io/privacy.html">Privacy Policy</a></p>
  </div>

  <div class="footer">
    <img src="data:image/png;base64," alt="Breathon"/>
    <p>© 2026 Breathon. All rights reserved.</p>
    <div class="footer-links">
      <a href="https://breathonapp.github.io/privacy.html">Privacy Policy</a>
      <a href="https://breathonapp.github.io/terms.html">Terms of Use</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
